%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raytheon's%20CEO%20said%20on%20an%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%20company%20stood%20to%20'benefit'%20from%20DoD%20budget%20increases%20due%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iron%20dome%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65387b070487ff031cad7788%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsraeli%20Iron%20Dome%20air%20defense%20system%20fires%20to%20intercept%20a%20rocket%20fired%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20in%20Ashkelon%2C%20Israel%2C%20Thursday%2C%20Oct.19%2C%202023.%20Since%20Israel%20activated%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20in%202011%2C%20the%20cutting-edge%20rocket-defense%20system%20has%20intercepted%20thousands%20of%20rockets%20fired%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20By%20Israeli%20military%20estimates%2C%20Hamas%20has%20already%20fired%207%2C000%20rockets%20into%20Israel%20during%20the%20current%20war.%3Cp%3E(AP%20Photo%2FTsafrir%20Abayov%2C%20File)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Biden%20requested%20an%20additional%20%24106%20billion%20to%20the%20DoD%20budget%2C%20citing%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20and%20other%20global%20conflicts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20CEO%20of%20military%20contractor%20RTX%20said%20Tuesday%20the%20company%20could%20%26quot%3Bbenefit%26quot%3B%20from%20an%20increased%20DoD%20budget.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERTX%20Corporation%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Raytheon%2C%20is%20a%20long-time%20US%20defense%20contractor%20which%20has%20worked%20on%20supplying%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%20since%202014.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20an%20October%2024%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fool.com%2Fearnings%2Fcall-transcripts%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Frtx-rtx-q3-2023-earnings-call-transcript%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Eearnings%20call%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20RTX%20Corporation%20CEO%20Greg%20Hayes%20said%20that%20the%20defense%20contractor%20stood%20to%20%26quot%3Bbenefit%26quot%3B%20from%20a%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense's%20budget%20increase%20which%20would%20fund%20the%20supply%20of%20weapons%20to%20Israel%20and%20the%20restocking%20of%20weapons%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20really%20across%20the%20entire%20Raytheon%20portfolio%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20a%20benefit%20of%20this%20restocking%2C%26quot%3B%20Hayes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fool.com%2Fearnings%2Fcall-transcripts%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Frtx-rtx-q3-2023-earnings-call-transcript%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20on%20the%20call%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%26quot%3BOn%20top%20of%20what%20we%20think%20is%20going%20to%20be%20an%20increase%20in%20DOD%20top%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20was%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20from%20Kristine%20Liwag%2C%20an%20analyst%20from%20Morgan%20Stanley.%20Liwag%20asked%20how%20quickly%20RTX%20Corporation%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Raytheon%20Corporation%2C%20could%20profit%20if%20Congress%20approves%20President%20Biden's%20request%20for%20a%20DoD%20budget%20increase%20in%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20this%20request%2C%20you've%20got%20equipment%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20air%20and%20missile%20defense%20for%20Israel%2C%20and%20replenishment%20of%20stockpile%20for%20both%2C%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fool.com%2Fearnings%2Fcall-transcripts%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Frtx-rtx-q3-2023-earnings-call-transcript%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3ELiwang%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20seems%20to%20fit%20quite%20nicely%20with%20the%20Raytheon%20Defense%20portfolio.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Morgan%20Stanley%20did%20not%20return%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%20A%20representative%20for%20RTX%20Corporation%20declined%20to%20comment%2C%20but%20pointed%20Insider%20to%20Hayes's%20October%2024%20CNBC%20interview%2C%20in%20which%20he%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20strong%20demand%26quot%3B%20for%20RTX%20products%20from%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bother%20partner%20countries%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20war%20in%20Gaza%20or%20in%20Israel%2C%20again%2C%20a%20tragic%20situation%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it%20will%20eventually%20lead%20to%20additional%20orders%2C%20most%20likely%2C%26quot%3B%20Hayes%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20focus%20right%20now%20is%20how%20do%20we%20support%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Force%3F%20How%20do%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20have%20what%20they%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20defend%20their%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2023%2F10%2F08%2Fisrael-attack-what-is-the-iron-dome-and-how-does-it-work%2F920a8e92-65d8-11ee-9753-2b3742e96987_story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%202014%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20RTX%20Corporation%20has%20been%20working%20with%20Israeli%20company%20Rafael%20Advanced%20Defense%20Systems%20to%20help%20produce%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%2C%20which%20detects%20and%20shoots%20down%20incoming%20rockets.%20The%20DoD%20has%20been%20funding%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2023%2F10%2F08%2Fisrael-attack-what-is-the-iron-dome-and-how-does-it-work%2F920a8e92-65d8-11ee-9753-2b3742e96987_story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Esince%202011%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20few%20years%20after%20Israel%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F09%2Fworld%2Firon-dome-israel-defe