ours%20later%20as%20chairman%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20two%20Odisha%20government%20initiatives%20with%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20rank%2C%20the%20latest%20development%20is%20a%20sure%20sign%20that%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20journey%20in%20public%20life%20is%20set%20for%20a%20fresh%20and%20frenzied%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20not%20made%20a%20functionary%20of%20the%20ruling%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20yet%2C%20there%20is%20little%20to%20doubt%20that%20Pandian%20hereafter%20will%20publicly%20dabble%20in%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20he%20did%20earlier%20only%20furtively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20by%20virtue%20of%20being%20the%20closest%20confidant%20of%20the%20ageing%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20will%20be%20seen%20as%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20possible%20successor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhether%20Pandian%20ultimately%20succeeds%20or%20not%20is%20an%20altogether%20different%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20normal%20circumstances%2C%20few%20would%20have%20given%20Pandian%20very%20little%20realistic%20chance.%20A%20Tamilian%20by%20birth%20who%20came%20to%20be%20posted%20in%20Odisha%20only%20after%20marrying%20an%20Odia%20IAS%20officer%2C%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98outsider%E2%80%99%20status%20should%20have%20ordinarily%20ruled%20him%20out%20for%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20top%20elected%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Odisha%20in%20the%20past%20decade%20or%20so%20has%20witnessed%20a%20rather%20abnormal%20administrative%20arrangement.%20Under%20it%2C%20the%20elected%20CM%20has%20gradually%20receded%20to%20the%20background%20with%20all%20levers%20of%20state%20power%20being%20increasingly%20wielded%20by%20his%20secretary.%20It%20has%20made%20Pandian%20extremely%20powerful.%20Having%20packed%20the%20ruling%20party%20leadership%20with%20his%20men%2C%20his%20word%20is%20law.%20Even%20bureaucrats%20senior%20to%20him%20defer%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20both%20the%20party%20and%20the%20state%20machinery%20firmly%20under%20his%20control%2C%20the%20dice%20will%20be%20loaded%20in%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20favour%20if%20he%20is%20to%20really%20pitch%20to%20take%20over%20the%20party%20when%20Patnaik%20exits%20the%20political%20stage.%20As%20social%20media%20posts%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20his%20retirement%20show%2C%20there%20is%20no%20dearth%20of%20sycophants%20in%20the%20BJD.%20Most%20members%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20are%20hailing%20Pandian%20as%20the%20new%20%E2%80%98messiah%E2%80%99%20under%20whose%20leadership%20the%20state%20apparently%20will%20flourish%20and%20advance%20like%20never%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20opponents%20of%20the%20BJD%20say%20nothing%20is%20impossible%20in%20Odisha%2C%20a%20state%20which%20in%20the%20early%201960s%20had%20a%20Bengali%20chief%20minister%20in%20one%20Biren%20Mitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20when%20Patnaik%20himself%20took%20over%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20spoke%20no%20Odia.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20him%20from%20ruling%20the%20state%20for%20the%20next%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20popular%20Patnaik%20solidly%20by%20his%20side%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20Pandian%20too%20may%20manage%20to%20secure%20enough%20public%20acceptability.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPandian%20stands%20to%20gain%20by%20quitting%20the%20IAS.%20Though%20all-powerful%2C%20he%20has%20rubbed%20too%20many%20senior%20bureaucrats%20the%20wrong%20way%20by%20bossing%20over%20them.%20These%20angry%20seniors%20would%20have%20made%20his%20continuation%20in%20the%20IAS%20impossible%20when%20Patnaik%20is%20not%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolitics%20holds%20out%20better%20prospects%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20is%2C%20his%20public%20profile%20has%20shot%20up%20immensely%20since%20he%20crisscrossed%20the%20state%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20hearing%20public%20grievances%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20chief%20minister.%20His%20travels%20in%20helicopters%20and%20elaborate%20convoys%20kicked%20up%20a%20political%20controversy%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-soumya-ranjan-patnaik-expelled-media-baron%5C%22%3Ecritics%20accusing%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20over-stepping%20his%20authority.%20But%20they%20also%20allowed%20Pandian%20to%20connect%20with%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people.%20The%20message%20too%20has%20gone%20out%20that%20Pandian%20is%20trusted%20by%20Patnaik.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20huge%20political%20capital%20that%20Pandian%20surely%20will%20bank%20upon.%20A%20bachelor%2C%20Patnaik%20has%20no%20designated%20successor.%20And%20should%20he%20ever%20publicly%20bat%20for%20Pandian%2C%20then%20that%20becomes%20a%20done%20deal%20with%20Pandian%20becoming%20the%20sole%20repository%20of%20all%20the%20goodwill%20that%20exists%20for%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20there%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20gap%20between%20the%20lip%20and%20the%20cup%20and%20Pandian%20needs%20to%20tread%20cautiously.%20Though%20it%20is%20for%20sure%20that%20men%20and%20women%20who%20will%20get%20BJD%20tickets%20to%20contest%20the%202024%20elections%20will%20mostly%20be%20his%20chosen%20ones%2C%20there%20are%20surely%20some%20leaders%20in%20the%20party%20who%20have%20not%20taken%20his%20meteoric%20rise%20kindly.%20In%20a%20scenario%20when%20Patnaik%20is%20not%20around%2C%20they%20may%20not%20keep%20quiet%20and%20meekly%20accept%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20will%20be%20then.%20For%20now%2C%20the%20Patnaik-Pandian%20duo%20is%20succeeding%20in%20controlling%20the%20circumstances.%20They%20are%20creating%20situations%20and%20then%20setting%20the%20political%20narrative%20that%20the%20opposition%20is%20struggling%20to%20challenge.%20They%20have%20not%20even%20been%20able%20to%20turn%20the%20tables%20over%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20emergence.%20Though%20Odias%20may%20not%20be%20overwhelmingly%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20secretary%20reigning%20supreme%2C%20they%20have%20not%20voiced%20their%20displeasure%20strongly%20as%20well.%20The%20ambivalence%20allows%20Pandian%20and%20h