681.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Israel's%20Ground%20Invasion%20Of%20Gaza%2C%20Biden%20Said%20This%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmidst%20reports%20of%20an%20imminent%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20by%20Israel%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20said%20that%20Israel%20can%20make%20its%20own%20decisions%2C%20as%20the%20US%20firmly%20backs%20its%20ally%20while%20urging%20caution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20conflict%20was%20triggered%20by%20unprecedented%20attacks%20against%20Israel%20by%20Hamas%20militants%20on%20October%207%2C%20killing%20more%20than%201%2C400%20people.%20Israel%20has%20launched%20a%20massive%20counter-offensive%20against%20the%20Islamic%20militant%20group%20that%20has%20ruled%20Gaza%20since%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20made%20the%20comment%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20while%20posing%20for%20a%20picture%20with%20the%20visiting%20Australian%20Prime%20Minister%20Anthony%20Albanese.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20urging%20Israel%20to%20delay%20its%20ground%20invasion%3F%26quot%3B%20Biden%20was%20asked%2C%20to%20which%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Israelis%20can%20make%20their%20own%20decisions.%26quot%3B%20Last%20week%2C%20Israeli%20Defence%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20laid%20out%20the%20Jewish%20nation's%20plan%20to%20change%20the%20%26quot%3Bsecurity%20regime%26quot%3B%20in%20Gaza--%20implying%20Hamas'%20removal--%20and%20said%20the%20plan%20was%20designed%20in%20three%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGallant%20said%20that%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20(IFD)%20was%20in%20the%20plan's%20first%20stage%20when%20it%20was%20carrying%20out%20aerial%20strikes.%20It%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20ground%20incursion%20and%20finally%2C%20the%20change%20of%20security%20regime%20in%20Gaza%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%205%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20so%20far%2C%20including%20over%202%2C000%20children%20and%201%2C100%20women%2C%20as%20well%20as%20journalists%2C%20medical%20workers%20and%20first%20responders%2C%20with%20more%20than%2016%2C000%20injured%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJohn%20Kirby%2C%20Coordinator%20for%20Strategic%20Communications%20at%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20US%20will%20continue%20to%20ensure%20that%20Israel%20has%20the%20tools%20and%20capabilities%20it%20needs%20to%20defend%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20try%20to%20get%20that%20humanitarian%20assistance%20in%2C%20and%20we're%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20try%20to%20get%20hostages%20and%20people%20out%20of%20Gaza%20appropriately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20ceasefire%20right%20now%20really%20only%20benefits%20Hamas.%20That's%20where%20we%20are%20right%20now.%20And%20I%20understand%20the%20question%2C%20but%20I'm%20just%20not%20going%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20where%20things%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20talk%20to%20our%20Israeli%20counterparts%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20avoiding%20and%20minimizing%20civilian%20casualties%20and%20respecting%20innocent%20life%20and%20trying%20to%20prevent%20collateral%20damage%20as%20they%20go%20after%20legitimate%20Hamas%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20war%2C%20it%20is%20combat%2C%20it%20is%20bloody%2C%20it%20is%20ugly%2C%20and%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20messy%20and%20innocent%20civilians%20are%20going%20to%20be%20hurt%20going%20forward.%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20tell%20you%20something%20different.%20I%20wish%20that%20wasn't%20going%20to%20happen%2C%20but%20it%20is%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20doesn't%20make%20it%20right%2C%20it%20doesn't%20make%20it%20dismiss