C%20who%20was%20attending%20the%20trial%2C%20watched%20from%20the%20defense%20table%20as%20the%20judge%20presiding%20over%20the%20trial%2C%20New%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Arthur%20Engoron%2C%20quickly%20interrupted%20Habba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20speeches%2C%26quot%3B%20Engoron%20warned%2C%20noting%20that%20as%20a%20lawyer%2C%20Habba%20must%20ask%20questions%2C%20not%20make%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHabba%20responded%20with%20another%20statement.%20%26quot%3BNo%20speeches.%20That%20goes%20both%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20though%20it%20was%20unclear%20if%20she%20was%20agreeing%20with%20the%20judge%2C%20or%20deflecting%20his%20directive%20onto%20Cohen%2C%20or%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHabba%20is%20expected%20to%20continue%20her%20cross-examination%20of%20Cohen%20on%20Wednesday%20morning.%20She%20got%20in%20only%20a%20half%20hour%20of%20cross%20before%20court%20ended%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20that%20half%20hour%2C%20she%20called%20Cohen%20a%20liar%20and%20perjuror%20in%20multiple%20questions%20%E2%80%93%20%26quot%3Bso%20you%20have%20lied%20under%20oath%20numerous%20times%2C%20Mr.%20Cohen%3F%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20typical%20query%2C%20as%20was%20%26quot%3BSo%20you%20lied%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20Cohen's%20credibility%20%E2%80%93%20called%20%26quot%3Bimpeaching%26quot%3B%20a%20witness%20in%20legal%20parlance%20%E2%80%93%20was%20not%20surprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20is%20one%20the%20former%20president's%20most%20legally%20dangerous%20opponents%2C%20given%20his%20key%20role%20in%20both%20the%20ongoing%20Manhattan%20fraud%20trial%20and%20a%20felony%20%26quot%3Bhush-money%26quot%3B%20case%20scheduled%20for%20March%20in%20a%20courthouse%20just%20a%20block%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Cohen%20is%20vulnerable%20to%20perjury%20accusations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20flipping%20against%20Trump%2C%20his%20former%20client%20and%20employer%2C%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmichael-cohen-plea-deal-reveals-most-pivotal-time-of-2016-election-trump-russia-events-2018-11%5C%22%3ECohen%20admitted%20he%20lied%20to%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20then-president's%20plan%20to%20build%20a%20Trump%20Tower%20in%20Moscow%20during%20the%202016%20election.%20Cohen%20has%20since%20further%20admitted%20that%20he%20lied%20to%20a%20federal%20judge%20when%20he%20pleaded%20guilty%20in%202019%20to%20federal%20tax%20evasion%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20one%20point%2C%20Habba%20dragged%20Cohen's%20wife%20into%20the%20cross%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20you%20ever%20tell%20your%20wife%20that%20you%20were%20committing%20perjury%3F%26quot%3B%20in%20the%202019%20tax%20plea%2C%20Habba%20asked%20Cohen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20minute%2C%20a%20figurative%20game%20of%20courtroom%20musical%20chairs%20ensued%2C%20with%20Cohen%20behaving%20like%20a%20lawyer%20instead%20of%20a%20witness%2C%20Habba%20behaving%20like%20a%20judge%20instead%20of%20a%20lawyer%2C%20and%20the%20real%20judge%20struggling%20to%20keep%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObjection!%26quot%3B%20Cohen%2C%20a%20former%20lawyer%20with%20a%20revoked%20law%20license%2C%20answered%20Habba's%20%26quot%3Bdid%20you%20ever%20tell%20your%20wife%26quot%3B%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20you%20don't%20get%20to%20object.%26quot%3B%20Habba%20told%20him%2C%20noting%20correctly%20that%20only%20lawyers%20can%20do%20that%2C%20but%20acting%20like%20a%20judge%20in%20saying%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20the%20attorney%20general's%20lawyers%20objected%20to%20the%20objection%2C%20and%20lead%20defense%20lawyer%20Christopher%20Kise%20rushed%20to%20Habba's%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20serial%20liar%2C%26quot%3B%20Kise%20said%20of%20Cohen.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20he%20lied%20to%20his%20wife%2C%20that%20is%20relevant%20to%20impeachment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssistant%20Attorney%20General%20Colleen%20Fahe