Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20orange%20cushion%20representing%20a%20closed%20toilet%20seat%20in%20a%20white%2C%20futuristic%20bathroom%20with%20windows%20looking%20out%20into%20space%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6535884896908fd7cdb4d91d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESpace%20Perspective%20says%20it%20will%20unveil%20the%20world's%20first%20space%20spa%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fancy%20bathroom.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Space%20Perspectives%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%201%2C650%20people%20have%20purchased%20%24125%2C000%20tickets%20with%20the%20company%20to%20explore%20the%20upper%20echelons%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-launch-hole-ionosphere-earth-atmosphere-physicist-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEarth's%20atmosphere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecial%20training%20for%20passengers%20will%20not%20be%20required%2C%20Space%20Perspective%20said.%20All%20they%20have%20to%20do%20is%20sign%20some%20forms%2C%20take%20a%20seat%2C%20and%20strap%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20extravagant%20and%20cater%20to%20people%20with%20money%20to%20spend%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsee-the-high-risk-trips-wealthy-travelers-are-booking-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisk-taking%20adventures%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Christmas-ornament-shaped%20cabin%20is%20built%20with%20a%20space%20toilet%2C%20and%20meals%20and%20cocktails%20will%20be%20served%20during%20the%20flight%2C%20per%20Space%20Perspectives.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20looking%20to%20implement%20design%20elements%20from%20the%20Mercedes-Maybach%20suite%20of%20luxury%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20that%20goes%20on%20in%20people's%20minds%20when%20they%20think%20about%20how%20we%20fly%20to%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Poynter%20said.%