nd%2C%20Barnsley%2C%20after%20he%20started%20to%20cry.%20The%2010-month-old%20remains%20in%20the%20hospital%20in%20a%20stable%20but%20serious%20condition%2C%20officials%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20called%20at%207.42am%20this%20morning%20to%20a%20property%20in%20Hoyland%2C%20following%20a%20young%20child%20being%20attacked%20and%20bitten%20by%20a%20family%20dog%2C%26quot%3B%20Dog%20Legislation%20Officer%20PC%20Paul%20Jameson%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-south-yorkshire-67209689%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Mr%20Jameson%20added%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20out%20of%20character%20for%20the%20dog%2C%20who%20has%20no%20previous%20history%20of%20aggression.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20early%20enquiries%20with%20the%20family%20highlighted%20that%20the%20dog%20was%20not%20previously%20reported%20to%20be%20of%20an%20aggressive%20nature%2C%20and%20this%20was%20a%20family%20who%20took%20precautions%20and%20are%20responsible%20owners%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fhome-news%2Fdog-attack-baby-barnsley-police-b2435157.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20baby's%20family%20said%20that%20their%20dog%20had%20never%20shown%20any%20signs%20of%20aggression%20before%20the%20horrifying%20incident.%20According%20to%20them%2C%20the%20animal%20is%20normally%20%26quot%3Bpleasant%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Baffectionate%26quot%3B%20with%20children.%20However%2C%20the%20family%20added%20that%20the%20dog%20may%20have%20become%20stressed%20by%20fireworks%20being%20set%20off%20in%20the%20local%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20incident%20like%20this%20is%20a%20stark%20reminder%20that%20regardless%20of%20a%20dog's%20nature%2C%20or%20previous%20interactions%20with%20children%2C%20other%20dogs%20and%20people%2C%20they%20are%20animals%20and%20their%20innate%20instinct%20to%20protect%20themselves%20which%20can%20result%20in%20serious%20injuries%20and%20sometimes%20fatality%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jameson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fman-sells-energy-drink-made-from-urine-on-amazon-company-calls-it-crude-stunt-4510514%5C%22%3EMan%20Sells%20%26quot%3BEnergy%20Drink%26quot%3B%20Made%20From%20Urine%20On%20Amazon%2C%20Company%20Calls%20It%20%26quot%3BCrude%20Stunt%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20further%20urged%20owners%20to%20watch%20out%20for%20changes%20in%20their%20dog's%20behaviour%20at%20this%20time%20of%20the%20year%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20a%20space%20they%20feel%20safe%2C%20away%20from%20children%20and%20people.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20know%20your%20dog%20does%20not%20accept%20people%20knocking%20at%20the%20door%2C%20put%20up%20a%20sign%20ahead%20of%20Halloween%20to%20stop%20people%20knocking%2C%26quot%3B%20PC%20Jameson%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20dog%20becomes%20unsettled%20when%20fireworks%20are%20set%20off%2C%20walk%20your%20dog%20in%20daylight%20hours%2C%20close%20the%20windows%20and%20draw%20your%20curtains%20to%20help%20muffle%20the%20sound%20and%20put%20the%20radio%20or%20TV%20on.%20Leave%20toys%20in%20the%20area%20your%20dog%20associates%20with%20feeling%20calm%20and%20safe.%20If%20you're%20hosting%20a%20celebration%2C%20follow%20the%20tips%20on%20our%20leaflet%20to%20keep%20everyone%20in%20your%20home%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20a%20Cane%20Corso%20is%20a%20breed%20of%20mastiff%20descended%20from%20Molossian%20war%20dogs%20of%20ancient%20Rome.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698169020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fndd032vg_cane-corso-_625x300_24_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F10-month-old-baby-in-uk-seriou