3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkaran-johar-on-shah-rukh-khan-he-never-liked-love-stories-but-preferred-action-movies%2Farticleshow%2F104680212.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20States%20Sue%20Facebook%20Owner%20Meta%20Over%20Harm%20To%20Children's%20Mental%20Health%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20US%20states%20are%20suing%20Meta%20Platforms%20and%20its%20Instagram%20unit%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20contributing%20to%20a%20youth%20mental%20health%20crisis%20through%20the%20addictive%20nature%20of%20their%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20complaint%20filed%20in%20the%20Oakland%2C%20California%2C%20federal%20court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%2033%20states%20including%20California%20and%20Illinois%20said%20Meta%2C%20which%20also%20operates%20Facebook%2C%20has%20repeatedly%20misled%20the%20public%20about%20the%20substantial%20dangers%20of%20its%20platforms%20and%20knowingly%20induced%20young%20children%20and%20teenagers%20into%20addictive%20and%20compulsive%20social%20media%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResearch%20has%20shown%20that%20young%20people's%20use%20of%20Meta's%20social%20media%20platforms%20is%20associated%20with%20depression%2C%20anxiety%2C%20insomnia%2C%20interference%20with%20education%20and%20daily%20life%2C%20and%20many%20other%20negative%20outcomes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20legal%20actions%20against%20social%20media%20companies%20on%20behalf%20of%20children%20and%20teens.%20ByteDance's%20TikTok%20and%20Google's%20YouTube%20are%20also%20the%20subjects%20of%20the%20hundreds%20of%20lawsuits%20filed%20on%20behalf%20of%20children%20and%20school%20districts%20about%20the%20addictiveness%20of%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeta%20has%20harnessed%20powerful%20and%20unprecedented%20technologies%20to%20entice%2C%20engage%2C%20and%20ultimately%20ensnare%20youth%20and%20teens%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%20%26quot%3BIts%20motive%20is%20profit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20seeks%20a%20variety%20of%20remedies%2C%20including%20substantial%20civil%20penalties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeta%20said%20that%20it%20had%20sought%20to%20make%20young%20people%20safe%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20disappointed%20that%20instead%20of%20working%20productively%20with%20companies%20across%20the%20industry%20to%20create%20clear%2C%20age-appropriate%20standards%20for%20the%20many%20apps%20teens%20use%2C%20the%20attorneys%20general%20have%20chosen%20this%20path%2C%26quot%3B%20Meta%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeta%20shares%20declined%20slightly%20after%20the%20states'%20lawsuit%20was%20made%20public%20and%20were%20down%200.3%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20focus%20on%20Meta%20stems%20from%20the%20release%20of%20documents%20in%202021%20that%20showed%20that%20Meta%20had%20data%20showing%20that%20Instagram%2C%20which%20began%20as%20a%20photo-sharing%20app%2C%20was%20addictive%20and%20worsens%20body%20image%20issues%20for%20some%20teen%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20Meta%20strives%20to%20ensure%20that%20young%20people%20spend%20as%20much%20time%20as%20possible%20on%20social%20media%20despite%20knowing%20that%20teenage%20brains%20are%20susceptible%20to%20the%20need%20for%20approval%20in%20the%20form%20of%20%26quot%3Blikes%26quot%3B%20from%20other%20users%20about%20their%20content.%20Meta%20deceptively%20denied%20publicly%20that%20its%20social%20media%20was%20harmful%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20recently%20as%202020%2C%20Meta%20continued%20to%20intentionally%20design%20its%20platforms%20to%20manipulate%20dopamine%20responses%20in%20its%20young%20users%20to%20maximize%20time%20spent%20on%20its%20platforms.%20Meta%20did%20not%20disclose%20that%20its%20algorithms%20were%20designed%20to%20capitalize%20on%20young%20users'%20dopamine%20responses%20and%20create%20an%20addictive%20cycle%20of%20engagement%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDopamine%20is%20a%20type%20of%20neurotransmitter%20that%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20feelings%20of%20pleasure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20Meta%20also%20violated%20a%20law%20banning%20the%20collection%20of%20data%20of%20children%20under%20age%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20action%20seeks%20to%20patch%20holes%20left%20by%20the%20U.S.%20Congress'%20inability%20to%20pass%20new%20online%20protections%20for%20children%2C%20despite%20years%20of%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20also%20alleged%20that%20Meta%20was%20seeking%20to%20expand%20what%20the%20states%20say%20are%20harmful%20practices%20into%20virtual%20reality%2C%20including%20Meta's%20Horizon%20Worlds%20platform%20as%20well%20as%20the%20communications%20apps%20WhatsApp%20and%20Messenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeta%20has%20been%20harming%20our%20children%20and%20teens%2C%20cultivating%20addiction%20to%20boost%20corporate%20profits%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20California%20Attorney%20General%20Rob%20Bonta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20general%20for%20New%20Hampshire%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC%20both%20said%20that%20they%20have%20filed%20related%20lawsuits%20in%20local%20courts.%20Seven%20other%20states%20are%20expected%20to%20file%20similar%20lawsuits%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20number%20of%20states%20suing%20to%2042.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Menlo%20Park%2C%20California%2C%20company%20and%20other%20social%20media%20companies%20already%20face%20hundreds%20of%20lawsuits%20brought%20on%20behalf%20of%20children%20and%20school%20districts%20raising%20similar%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698167820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%