l%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Finstagram-linked-to-depression-anxiety-insomnia-in-kids-claims-lawsuit-123102400977_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Finstagram-linked-to-depression-anxiety-insomnia-in-kids-claims-lawsuit-123102400977_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22700%20Palestinians%20Killed%20In%20Overnight%20Israeli%20Strikes%2C%20Says%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20700%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20overnight%20by%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%2C%20Gaza's%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20said%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20highest%2024-hour%20death%20toll%20in%20Israel's%20two-week-old%20%26quot%3Btotal%20siege%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20pressure%20grew%20for%20aid%20to%20be%20allowed%20into%20the%20enclave%20unimpeded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20it%20had%20hit%20over%20400%20Hamas%20targets%20and%20killed%20dozens%20of%20its%20fighters%20overnight%2C%20but%20that%20it%20would%20take%20time%20to%20destroy%20Gaza's%20ruling%20Islamist%20group%2C%20whose%20deadly%20cross-border%20attack%20on%20October%207%20shocked%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20international%20aid%20agencies%20warning%20of%20a%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%20unfolding%20in%20Gaza%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20flew%20to%20Israel%20to%20offer%20it%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMacron%20told%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20that%20France%20stood%20%26quot%3Bshoulder%20to%20shoulder%26quot%3B%20with%20Israel%20in%20its%20war%20with%20Hamas%20but%20that%20it%20must%20not%20fight%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20rules%26quot%3B.%20Netanyahu%20said%20Israel%20would%20try%20to%20protect%20civilians%20as%20it%20worked%20to%20ensure%20they%20%26quot%3Bwill%20no%20longer%20live%20under%20Hamas%20tyranny%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnited%20Nations%20agencies%20called%20%26quot%3Bon%20our%20knees%26quot%3B%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20emergency%20aid%20to%20be%20allowed%20unimpeded%20into%20Gaza%2C%20saying%20more%20than%2020%20times%20current%20deliveries%20were%20needed%20to%20support%20its%20Palestinian%20population%20after%20two%20weeks%20of%20Israeli%20bombardment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%2C%20in%20the%20latest%20of%20increasingly%20desperate%20UN%20appeals%2C%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Ban%20immediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%26quot%3B%20to%20allow%20safe%20deliveries%20of%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDoctors%20in%20Gaza%20say%20patients%20arriving%20at%20hospitals%20are%20showing%20signs%20of%20disease%20caused%20by%20overcrowding%20and%20poor%20sanitation%20after%20more%20than%201.4%20million%20people%20fled%20their%20homes%20for%20temporary%20shelters%20under%20Israel's%20heaviest-ever%20bombardment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20appeared%20to%20be%20little%20prospect%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20any%20time%20soon%20in%20the%20bloodiest%20episode%20in%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict%20for%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaza's%20health%20ministry%20said%20at%20least%205%2C791%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20bombardments%20of%20the%20densely%20populated%20territory%20since%20Oct.%207%2C%20including%202%2C360%20children.%20A%20total%20of%20704%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20previous%2024%20hours%20alone%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMinistry%20spokesman%20Ashraf%20Al-Qidra%20said%20it%20was%20the%20highest%2024-hour%20number%20of%20deaths%20in%20the%20two%20weeks%20of%20the%20Israeli%20bombing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20air%20strike%20in%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20Abdallah%20Tabash%20held%20his%20dead%20daughter%20Sidra%2C%20refusing%20to%20let%20go%20as%20he%20held%20her%20bloodstained%20face%20and%20hair.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20look%20at%20her%20as%20much%20as%20I%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20tanks%20and%20troops%20are%20massed%20on%20the%20border%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20enclave%20awaiting%20orders%20for%20an%20expected%20ground%20invasion%20-%20an%20operation%20that%20may%20be%20complicated%20by%20fears%20for%20the%20hostages'%20welfare%20and%20militants%20heavily%20armed%20by%20Iran%20dug%20into%20a%20crowded%20urban%20setting%20using%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bombardments%20were%20unleashed%20in%20response%20to%20a%20shock%20cross-border%20Hamas%20assault%20into%20southern%20Israel%20in%20which%20gunmen%20killed%20over%201%2C400%20people%20-%20mostly%20civilians%20-%20in%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'I've%20been%20through%20hell'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20on%20Monday%20freed%20two%20Israeli%20women%20who%20were%20among%20the%20more%20than%20200%20hostages%20taken%20during%20the%20rampage%20-%20the%20third%20and%20fourth%20to%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYocheved%20Lifshitz%2C%2085%2C%20said%20she%20was%20beaten%20by%20militants%20as%20she%20was%20abducted%20and%20had%20difficulty%20breathing.%20%26quot%3BThey%20stormed%20into%20our%20homes.%20They%20beat%20people.%20They%20kidnapped%20others%2C%20the%20old%20and%20the%20young%20without%20distinction%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20seated%20in%20a%20wheelchair%20and%20speaking%20in%20barely%20a%20whisper%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20through%20hell%2C%26quot%3B%20Lifshitz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInside%20Gaza%2C%20a%20group%20of%20hostages%20were%20led%20into%20what%20Lifshitz%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bspider's%20web%26quot%3B%20of%20damp%20tunnels%20and%20eventually%20reached%20a%20large%20hall%20where%2C%20under%2024-hour%20guard%2C%20a%20doctor%20visited%20every%20other%20day%20and%20brought%20them%20medicines%20they%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20treated%20us%20gently%20and%20met%20all%20our%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Ready%20and%20determined'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20targets%20Israel%20said%20it%20hit%20overnight%20was%20a%20tunnel%20that%20allowed%20Hamas%20to%20infiltrate%20Israel%20from%20the%20sea%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Hamas%20command%20centres%20in%20mosques%2C%20it%20said.%20Reuters%20could%20not%20verify%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWide%20areas%20of%20highly%20urbanised%20Gaza%20have%20been%20demolished%20by%20Israeli%20bombs%2C%20forcing%20more%20than%20half%20of%20its%202.3%20million%20people%20to%20seek%20shelter%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20territory.%20Food%2C%20clean%20water%2C%20medicine%20and%20fuel%20are%20fast%20running%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResidents%20said%20several%20people%20were%20killed%20or%20wounded%20when%20an%20Israeli%20missile%20hit%20a%20petrol%20station%20in%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20where%20people%20who%20fled%20the%20eastern%20side%20of%20the%20city%20were%20gathered%20to%20charge%20their%20devices%20and%20fill%20water%20canisters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20bombed%20them%20in%20their%20sleep%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Abdallah%20Abu%20Al-Atta%2C%20who%20lives%20by%20the%20petrol%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2040%20medical%20centres%20halted%20operations%20after%20they%20ran%20out%20of%20fuel%20or%20were%20damaged%20by%20Israeli%20bombing%2C%20the%20health%20ministry%20spokesman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20Green%20light'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20soon%20Israel%20might%20launch%20a%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20remains%20unclear.%20The%20Middle%20East's%20most%20powerful%20military%20faces%20a%20group%20that%20has%20built%20up%20a%20powerful%20arsenal%20with%20Iran's%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorld%20powers%20are%20concerned%20the%20conflict%20could%20ignite%20the%20entire%20region%20and%20some%20have%20urged%20Israel%20to%20exercise%20restraint%2C%20while%20affirming%20its%20right%20to%20self-defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20is%20unclear%3A%20Palestinian%20hopes%20for%20an%20independent%20state%20in%20Israeli-o