news%2Fishaan-khatter-on-hollywood-debut-the-perfect-couple-hopefully-it-will-open-up-new-doors%2Farticleshow%2F104676863.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parliament's%20Public%20Accounts%20Committee%20to%20be%20Briefed%20on%20CAG%20Reports%20on%20Wednesday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16103200%2FGlimpses_of_the_new_Parliament_Building_in_New_Delhi_2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Public%20Accounts%20Committee%20(PAC)%20is%20expected%20to%20meet%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2025%2C%20when%20it%20will%20be%20briefed%20on%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20reports%20presented%20in%20parliament%20during%20the%20monsoon%20session.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20PAC%20is%20at%20present%20headed%20by%20Congress%20MP%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20and%20includes%2021%20other%20parliamentarians%20from%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20PAC%20is%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20parliamentary%20committees%20in%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIts%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Floksabha.nic.in%2Fwritereaddata%2Four%2520parliament%2FPublic%2520Accounts%2520committee.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efunctions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20include%20the%20examination%20of%20the%20Appropriation%20Accounts%20relating%20to%20the%20Railways%2C%20Defence%20Services%2C%20Postal%20Services%20and%20other%20Civil%20Ministries%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20Reports%20of%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor-General%20of%20India%20thereon%20as%20also%20the%20Reports%20of%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor-General%20on%20Revenue%20Receipts%20mainly%20form%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20deliberations%20of%20the%20Committee.%20The%20Committee%20may%2C%20also%20take%20up%20subjects%20relating%20to%20public%20finances%20for%20detailed%20examination%2C%20which%20are%20not%20specifically%20included%20in%20the%20Audit%20Reports.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20scrutinising%20the%20Reports%20of%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor-General%20on%20Revenue%20Receipts%2C%20the%20Committee%20examines%20various%20aspects%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20tax%20administration.%20The%20Committee%2C%20thus%2C%20examines%20cases%20involving%20under-assessments%2C%20tax%20evasion%2C%20non-levy%20of%20duties%2C%20misclassifications%2C%20etc.%2C%20identifies%20the%20loopholes%20in%20the%20taxation%20laws%20and%20procedures%20and%20makes%20recommendations%20in%20order%20to%20check%20leakage%20of%20revenue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20monsoon%20session%20that%20ended%20on%20August%2011%2C%20saw%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-reports-government-corruption-tea-board-khadi-bsnl-swadesh-darshan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etabling%20of%20twelve%20CAG%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Ethat%20revealed%20corruption%20and%20irregularities%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20several%20Union%20government%20ministries%20and%20departments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECAG%20reports%20have%20been%20of%20special%20interest%20after%20the%20UPA%20government%20came%20under%20fire%20for%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2F2g-accused-acquitted-happened-scam-wasnt%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9C2G%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcoalgate-scam-ex-coal-secretary-h-c-gupta-sentenced-to-three-years-in-jail%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Ccoal%20block%20allocation%20scam%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20which%20were%20revealed%20when%20Vinod%20Rai%20was%20the%20CAG%2C%20and%20which%20had%20serious%20consequences%20for%20the%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20credibility.%3