ment%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F08234700%2FIMG_1535.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20has%20questioned%20whether%20%E2%80%9Cextremists%20from%20across%20the%20border%E2%80%9D%20were%20among%20those%20behind%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%203.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20Vijayadashami%20speech%20at%20the%20RSS%20headquarters%20in%20Nagpur%20on%20Tuesday%20(October%2024)%2C%20Bhagwat%20questioned%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20powers%E2%80%9D%20who%20may%20be%20taking%20advantage%20of%20such%20unrest%20and%20instability%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20look%20at%20the%20current%20situation%20of%20Manipur%2C%20this%20fact%20becomes%20obvious%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rss.org%2FEncyc%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2FVijayaDashami-2023-Speech.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20did%20this%20mutual%20discord%20and%20hatred%20suddenly%20erupt%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20had%20been%20peaceful%20for%20almost%20a%20decade%3F%20Were%20there%20extremists%20from%20across%20the%20border%20also%20among%20those%20who%20committed%20violence%3F%20Why%2C%20and%20by%20whom%2C%20was%20an%20attempt%20made%20to%20give%20a%20communal%20tinge%20to%20this%20mutual%20conflict%20between%20the%20Manipuri%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%2C%20who%20were%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20future%20of%20their%20existence%3F%20Who%20has%20a%20vested%20interest%20in%20trying%20to%20drag%20and%20besmirch%20an%20organisation%20like%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20which%20has%20been%20engaged%20in%20serving%20everyone%20without%20any%20bias%20for%20years%2C%20into%20this%20unfortunate%20incident%20without%20any%20reason%3F%20Which%20foreign%20powers%20may%20be%20interested%20in%20taking%20advantage%20of%20such%20unrest%20and%20instability%20in%20Manipur%2C%20located%20between%20Nagabhoomi%20and%20Mizoram%20in%20this%20border%20area%3F%20Does%20the%20geopolitics%20of%20Southeast%20Asia%20also%20have%20a%20role%20in%20these%20events%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EQuestioning%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinstigation%20of%20violence%E2%80%9D%20Bhagwat%20said%20that%20violence%20has%20prevailed%20in%20the%20north%20eastern%20state%20despite%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20government%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country%20and%20a%20state%20government%20that%20wanted%20peace%20and%20stability%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20there%20being%20a%20strong%20government%20in%20the%20country%2C%20on%20whose%20strength%20and%20instigation%20has%20this%20violence%20continued%20unabated%20for%20so%20many%20days%3F%20Why%20did%20this%20violence%20erupt%20and%20continue%20even%20though%20there%20was%20a%20state%20government%20that%20wanted%20to%20maintain%20the%20peace%20that%20had%20prevailed%20over%20the%20last%209%20years%3F%20Now%2C%20when%20people%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20conflict%20are%20seeking%20peace%2C%20which%20are%20these%20forces%20that%20are%20attempting%20to%20trigger%20hatred%20and%20violence%20by%20causing%20an%20incident%20as%20soon%20as%20any%20positive%20step%20is%20seen%20being%20taken%20in%20that%20direction%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20and%20Why%20Stopping%20It%20Poses%20a%20Test%20For%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhagwat%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmultidimensional%20efforts%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20required%20along%20with%20a%20strong%20political%20will%20and%20leadership%20in%20%E2%80%9Cbridging%20the%20gap%20of%20mutual%20distrust%20that%20has%20arisen%20due%20to%20the%20unfortunate%20situation%20between%20the%20two%20communities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20outbreak%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%2C%20more%20than%2070%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20and%20over%20170%20people%20have%20died.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20under%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%20for%20the%20continued%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20the%20central%20government%20has%20defended%20Singh%20under%20opposition%20fire%20and%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20his%20removal%20as%20he%20has%20been%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famit-shah-defends-biren-singh-in-parliament%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Ccooperative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20May%203%2C%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Churachandpur%20after%20a%20Kuki-led%20tribal%20solidarity%20march%20in%2010%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%2016%20districts.%20As%20the%20Meitei%20community%20organised%20counter-protests%20and%20blockades%2C%20clashes%20spread%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20violence%20was%20initially%20pitted%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20Manipur%20high%20court%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ruling%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20longstanding%20Meitei%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state%20in%20recent%20months%20has%20sought%20to%20shift%20the%20blame%20on%20outside%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn