s%20friend%2C%20Muzaffar%20Hussain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20Ramleela%2C%20Muslims%20perform%20various%20roles%20such%20as%20Lord%20Rama%2C%20Laxman%2C%20Sita%2C%20Janak%2C%20Dasharath%2C%20and%20many%20others.%20Just%20as%20Khan%20portrays%20the%20character%20of%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20Suhail%20Khan%20takes%20on%20the%20role%20of%20Laxman%2C%20while%20Farhan%20Ali%20portrays%20Sita.%20Bharat%20is%20played%20by%20Suhel%20Khan%2C%20and%20Sher%20Khan%20embodies%20the%20character%20of%20Janak.%20Even%20the%20role%20of%20young%20Ram%20is%20portrayed%20by%20Abdul%20Hasan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESalman%20Khan%20has%20been%20part%20of%20this%20Ramleela%20for%20the%20last%2012%20years.%20And%20it%20has%20been%20seven%20years%20since%20he%20has%20been%20performing%20on%20stage%20as%20Lord%20Rama.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20wear%20the%20crown%20and%20dress%20as%20the%20king%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20an%20aura%20of%20devotion%20envelops%20the%20scene.%20People%20feel%20that%20Lord%20Rama%20is%20physically%20present%20before%20them.%20Men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children%20shower%20flowers%20and%20seek%20blessings%20by%20touching%20my%20feet.%20During%20these%20moments%2C%20people%20seem%20to%20forget%20my%20real%20identity%20and%20perceive%20me%20as%20Lord%20Rama.%20Experiencing%20this%20atmosphere%20fills%20me%20with%20a%20profound%20sense%20of%20divine%20happiness%20and%20makes%20me%20feel%20as%20if%20I%20have%20embodied%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram%2C%20a%20rare%20feeling%2C%20I%20may%20not%20experience%20elsewhere.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20people%20in%20a%20small%20town%20like%20Bakshi%20ka%20Talab%20can%20coexist%20with%20brotherhood%20and%20solidarity%2C%20why%20do%20some%20individuals%20attempt%20to%20spread%20hatred%20across%20the%20entire%20country%2C%E2%80%9C%20says%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20a%20gym%20trainer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwenty-year%20old%20Sahil%20Khan%2C%20a%20student%2C%20who%20plays%20the%20role%20of%20Laxman%2C%20joined%20the%20Ramleela%20w