2023%2F10%2F24083208%2FF9JMon9WoAAF2wq.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOne%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20cricketers%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20(77)%20breathed%20his%20last%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2023.%20This%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%20Rajdeep%20Sardesai%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3EDemocracy%E2%80%99s%20XI%3A%20The%20Great%20Indian%20Cricket%20Story%3Cem%3E%2C%20published%20by%20Juggernaut%20in%202017.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%201966%2C%20when%20Bedi%20first%20represented%20India%2C%20to%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20his%20career%20in%20the%20late%201970s%2C%20India%20underwent%20a%20glorious%20spin%20revolution%20that%20would%20change%20Indian%20cricket%20forever.%20Brahma%2C%20the%20creator%20God%20in%20the%20Trimurti%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20has%20four%20faces%20looking%20in%20four%20different%20directions.%20But%20even%20he%20would%20have%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20recreate%20the%20magic%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20spin%20quartet%20which%20dominated%20the%20sport%20for%20a%20decade%20and%20more.%20And%20mirroring%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20unique%20notion%20of%20unity%20in%20diversity%2C%20the%20four%20Indian%20spinners%20were%20distinctive%20individuals%20with%20sharply%20contrasting%20personalities%20but%20united%20in%20their%20purpose%20of%20taking%20wickets%20for%20India.%20It%20was%20like%20having%20four%20magicians%20perform%20in%20one%20show%2C%20each%20with%20a%20unique%20bag%20of%20tricks%2C%20each%20luring%20an%20unsuspecting%20batsman%20to%20his%20doom%20with%20their%20mastery%20over%20flight%20and%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EErapalli%20Prasanna%2C%20who%20made%20his%20debut%20in%201962%2C%20was%20the%20oldest%20of%20the%20four.%20He%20was%20a%20true-blue%20Kannadiga%20born%20in%20Shimoga%2C%20another%20remote%20corner%20in%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20metro-centric%20geography%20at%20the%20time.%20As%20an%20off-spinner%2C%20he%20was%20almost%20a%20right-arm%20version%20of%20Bedi%2C%20shorter%20and%20stockier%20but%20with%20the%20same%20instinct%20to%20play%20mind%20games%20with%20batsmen%20through%20his%20control%20over%20the%20spinning%20ball.%20%E2%80%98We%20were%20like%20Siamese%20twins%20I%20guess%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20says%20with%20a%20chuckle.%20%E2%80%98We%20would%20share%20secrets%20and%20plot%20how%20to%20get%20a%20batsman%20out.%20It%20was%20almost%20as%20if%20we%20could%20read%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20minds.%E2%80%99%20Prasanna%20was%20a%20qualified%20engineer%2C%20even%20giving%20up%20the%20sport%20for%20five%20years%20after%20his%20first%20Test%20series%20because%20his%20father%20wanted%20him%20to%20complete%20his%20engineering%20degree%20first.%20%E2%80%98In%20those%20days%2C%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20studies%20first%2C%20then%20cricket.%20My%20father%2C%20who%20was%20a%20government%20servant%2C%20allowed%20me%20to%20go%20on%20my%20first%20cricket%20tour%20in%201962%20only%20because%20the%20Maharaja%20of%20Mysore%20intervened%20and%20promised%20him%20I%20would%20complete%20my%20degree%20on%20my%20return%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrasanna%E2%80%99s%20off-spinning%20rival%20was%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20Srinivas%20Venkataraghavan%2C%20another%20engineering%20graduate.%20Venkat%20fitted%20in%20with%20the%20stereotype%20of%20the%20stoic%2C%20unsmiling%20Tamil%20Brahmin%20and%20was%20a%20strict%20disciplinarian.%20I%20once%20met%20him%20at%20the%20Madras%20Cricket%20Club%20where%20he%20admonished%20a%20group%20of%20teenagers%20at%20the%20adjoining%20table%20for%20speaking%20too%20loudly.%20%E2%80%98He%20was%20the%20professor%2C%20the%20intellectual%20amongst%20us%20bon%20vivants.%20We%20would%20be%20having%20a%20drink%20and%20he%20would%20be%20reading%20a%20book%2C%E2%80%99%20says%20Bedi.%20Venkat%20was%20more%20than%20just%20a%20spinner%2C%20though%3B%20unlike%20the%20others%2C%20he%20was%20a%20decent%20batsman%20and%20a%20fine%20close-in%20fielder%20who%20would%20later%20even%20go%20on%20to%20become%20an%20international%20umpire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20maestro%20making%20up%20this%20incredible%20foursome%20was%20also%20the%20most%20enigmatic%20and%20fascinating.%20Bhagwat%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20another%20Kannadiga%2C%20was%20a%20truly%20heroic%20figure.%20An%20attack%20of%20polio%20at%20a%20very%20young%20age%20had%20withered%20his%20right%20arm%20but%20that%20did%20not%20stop%20him%20from%20becoming%2C%20arguably%2C%20the%20greatest%20match-winning%20bowler%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20history.%20He%20was%20unconventional%20in%20every%20sense%3B%20he%20would%20take%20a%20long%20run-up%20for%20a%20spinner%20and%20bowl%20leg-spinning%20deliveries%20with%20a%20pace%20and%20variety%20that%20foxed%20the%20best%20players.%20The%20sight%20of%20Chandrasekhar%20with%20the%20ball%2C%20marking%20his%20run-up%2C%20was%20enough%20for%20an%20entire%20stadium%20in%20Mumbai%20or%20Kolkata%20to%20shout%20in%20unison%2C%20%E2%80%98Boowwlled%E2%80%99.%20The%20sound%20would%20echo%20with%20a%20frenzy%20that%20would%20leave%20overseas%20batsmen%20shaken%20even%20before%20they%20played%20a%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Chandrasekhar%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20playing%20cricket%2C%20he%20liked%20to%20be%20far%20away%20from%20the%20action%2C%20quietly%20listening%20to%20a%20song%20by%20Mukesh%20or%20Saigal.%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20wanted%20to%20find%20Chandra%20before%20a%20Test%20match%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20he%20would%20be%20in%20Mukesh%E2%80%99s%20house%20for%20a%20private%20music%20concert%2C%E2%80%99%20recalls%20Bedi.%20Even%20now%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20prefers%20to%20be%20a%20recluse%2C%20refusing%20to%20carry%20a%20mobile%20%E2%80%93%20or%20at%20least%20choosing%20not%20to%20share%20the%20number!%20%E2%80%93%20and%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20his%20time%20with%20his%20son%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20ask%20Syed%20Kirmani%2C%20arguably%20the%20finest%20Indian%20wicketkeeper%20who%20played%20a%20fair%20bit%20with%20the%20four%20spinners%2C%20to%20compare%20them.%20%E2%80%98Champions%2C%20all%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%98Chandra%20was%20a%20genius%20and%20keeping%20to%20him%20was%20the%20biggest%20challenge.%20He%20could%20bowl%20leg-spin%2C%20googlies%20and%20top-spinners%20with%20almost%20the%20same%20action.%20And%20his%20faster%20one%20had%20the%20speed%20of%20a%20fast%20bowler.%20I%20remember%20he%20bowled%20a%20bouncer%20to%20Viv%20Richards%20once%20that%20went%20past%20the%20great%20batsman%E2%80%99s%20nose.%20Viv%20turned%20around%20and%20asked%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20this%20guy%20bowling%20spin%20or%20is%20he%20Jeff%20Thomson%20%5Bthe%20fastest%20bowler%20in%20the%20world%20in%20the%201970s%5D!%E2%80%9D%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20Bowled%20to%20Deceive%20but%2C%20Frank%20and%20Big-Hearted%2C%20Was%20the%20Least%20Deceptive%20of%20Men%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbishan-singh-bedi-bowled-to-deceive-but-frank-and-big-hearted-was-the-least-deceptive-of-men%5C%22%3EBishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20Bowled%20to%20Deceive%20but%2C%20Frank%20and%20Big-Hearted%2C%20Was%20the%20Least%20Deceptive%20of%20Men%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EContinues%20Kirmani%2C%20%E2%80%98Prasanna%20was%20a%20wily%20fox%20who%20would%20defeat%20you%20in%20the%20air.%20His%20loop%20was%20such%20as%20if%20he%20was%20holding%20the%20ball%20on%20a%20string%20like%20a%20puppet-master.%20Venkat%20was%20not%20in%20the%20same%20league%2C%20he%20was%20flatter%20with%20his%20deliveries%20but%20very%20exact%20and%20determined.%20And%20Bedi%20was%20simply%20poetry%20in%20action.%20He%20could%20bowl%20six%20different%20deliveries%20in%20an%20over%2C%20including%20an%20armer%2C%20with%20the%20most%20effortless%20style.%20When%20you%20watched%20him%20bowl%2C%20you%20felt%20as%20if%20you%20were%20in%20a%20museum%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20great%20artist.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20342px)%2085vw%2C%20342px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24103037%2F71-KeS04QIL._SL1400_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22342%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24103037%2F71-KeS04QIL._SL1400_.jpg%20777w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24103037%2F71-KeS04QIL._SL1400_-194x300.jpg%20194w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24103037%2F71-KeS04QIL._SL1400_-663x1024.jpg%20663w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681489%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22528%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERajdeep%20Sardesai%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EDemocracy%E2%80%99s%20XI%3A%20The%20Great%20Indian%20Cricket%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EJuggernaut%2C%202017%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20did%20India%20become%20the%20land%20of%20spinners%20while%20neighbouring%20Pakistan%20produced%20fast%20bowlers%3F%20The%20conventional%20explanation%20is%20the%20differing%20physical%20attributes%20of%20the%20two%20South%20Asian%20neighbours.%20The%20tall%20and%20muscular%20Pakistanis%20were%20seen%20to%20possess%20the%20physique%20to%20bowl%20fast%20while%20the%20less%20well-built%20Indians%20were%20more%20adept%20at%20bowling%20spin.%20I%20offer%20a%20slight%20variation%20to%20the%20theory.%20In%20India%2C%20cricket%20was%20an%20elite%20and%20urban%20middle-class%20sport%20till%20Kapil%20Dev%E2%80%99s%20team%20won%20the%201983%20World%20Cup%20and%20opened%20up%20the%20sport%20to%20a%20new%20generation.%20The%20Indian%20team%20was%20mostly%20full%20of%20players%20belonging%20to%20the%20Brahminical%20upper%20castes%20who%20perhaps%20considered%20fast%20bowling%20hard%20labour%2C%20especially%20in%20hot%20weather%20with%20unforgiving%20pitches.%20It%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20three%20of%20the%20four%20spinning%20greats%20were%20urban%20Brahmins%20and%20mostly%20vegetarian%20with%20the%20Jat%20Sikh%20Bedi%20the%20only%20exception.%20The%20image%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20as%20more%20learned%20and%20less%20physical%20fits%20in%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20spin%20bowling%20as%20an%20art%20form%20where%20mind%20scores%20over%20muscle.%20When%20I%20suggest%20this%20to%20Prasanna%2C%20he%20laughs.%20%E2%80%98We%20were%20vegetarian%20in%20our%20food%20habits%2C%20but%20strictly%20non-vegetarian%20when%20we%20were%20gobbling%20up%20opposing%20batsmen!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBetween%20them%2C%20the%20spin%20quartet%20picked%20up%20an%20astonishing%20853%20Test%20wickets.%20By%20contrast%2C%20the%20great%20West%20Indian%20fast%20bowling%20equivalent%20of%20Andy%20Roberts%2C%20Joel%20Garner%2C%20Michael%20Holding%20and%20Colin%20Croft%20put%20together%20had%20835%20wickets.%20Of%20the%2098%20Test%20matches%20in%20which%20one%20or%20more%20of%20the%20spinners%20played%20together%2C%20India%20won%2023%2C%20lost%2036%20and%20drew%2039%20games.%20If%20those%20aren%E2%80%99t%20striking%20figures%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20put%20them%20in%20context%20%E2%80%93%20India%20won%20only%207%20out%20of%2076%20Tests%20till%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20spinners.%20%E2%80%98I%20think%20they%20changed%20the%20way%20we%20played%20the%20game.%20Until%20the%20spinners%20came%2C%20our%20main%20aim%20was%20not%20to%20lose%20the%20match.%20Now%20we%20could%20think%20of%20actually%20trying%20to%20win%20games%2C%E2%80%99%20explains%20former%20India%20captain%20Ajit%20Wadekar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWadekar%20should%20know.%20He%20was%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20team%20that%20scored%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20victories%20over%20the%20West%20Indies%20and%20England%20between%201970%20and%201973%2C%20wins%20that%20catapulted%20Indian%20cricket%20on%20to%20the%20world%20stage.%20The%20finest%20performance%20was%20probably%20at%20the%20Oval%20in%20London%20in%201971%20when%20India%20defeated%20England%20on%20its%20home%20turf%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20This%20is%20how%20my%20late%20father%20Dilip%20Sardesai%20remembers%20the%20game.%20%E2%80%98The%20wicket%20was%20turning%20when%20Wadekar%20brought%20Chandra%20on%20to%20bowl.%20Chandra%20and%20I%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20horse%20races%20on%20the%20rest%20day%20of%20the%20match.%20A%20horse%20called%20Mildred%20won%20a%20race.%20When%20John%20Edrich%20came%20to%20bat%2C%20I%20told%20Chandra%3A%20%E2%80%9CIsko%20Mildred%20daal%20%5Bbowl%20him%20a%20Mildred%5D.%E2%80%9D%20He%20bowled%20the%20most%20vicious%20googly%20and%20shattered%20the%20stumps.%20After%20that%2C%20Chandra%20was%20unplayable%20and%20the%20English%20batsmen%20were%20psychologically%20destroyed.%20When%20we%20won%20the%20game%20the%20next%20day%2C%20it%20seemed%20as%20if%20every%20Indian%20living%20in%20England%20was%20at%20the%20Oval.%20One%20of%20them%20offered%20us%20free%20food%20and%20drink%20for%20life%20in%20his%20restaurant%20and%20named%20dishes%20after%20us!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20August%20day%20at%20the%20Oval%20in%201971%2C%20Indian%20cricket%20had%20tasted%20real%20freedom.%20Just%20months%20later%2C%20India%20would%20go%20to%20war%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20liberate%20Bangladesh%20in%20a%20decisive%20military%20triumph%20that%20renewed%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20self-confidence%2C%20earlier%20dented%20by%20the%20defeat%20in%20the%201962%20Sino-Indian%20war.%20Chandrasekhar%20picked%20up%206%20wickets%2C%20Venkat%202%20and%20Bedi%201.%20The%20mantra%20of%20non-violence%20as%20defined%20by%20spin%20had%20won%20the%20day%20for%20the%20Indians%20yet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20match-winning%20performances%20would%20continue%20for%20at%20least%20another%20seven%20years%20till%20the%20fingers%20and%20arms%20began%20to%20tire.%20The%20great%20Indian%20spin%20quartet%20was%20conquered%20on%20the%20first%20tour%20to%20Pakistan%20in%201978.%20The%20host%20team%E2%80%99s%20batting%2C%20led%20by%20Zaheer%20Abbas%20and%20Javed%20Miandad%2C%20was%20in%20prime%20form%20on%20flat%20batting%20tracks%20and%20the%20ageing%20Indian%20bowling%20attack%20just%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20match%20up.%20The%20spinners%20would%20be%20quickly%20pushed%20into%20retirement.%20%E2%80%98It%20happened%20a%20little%20suddenly%20and%20was%20unfortunate%20but%20we%20had%20a%20bloody%20good%20ride%20along%20the%20way%2C%E2%80%99%20Prasanna%20reflects%20on%20the%20endgame.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEngland%20would%20be%20the%20venue%20of%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20final%20series%20in%201979.%20He%20was%20only%20thirty-three%20when%20he%20played%20his%20last%20Test%2C%20a%20relatively%20young%20age%20for%20a%20spinner.%20But%20no%20one%20had%20bowled%20more%20overs%20through%20the%201970s%20than%20the%20sardar%20from%20Amritsar.%20No%20one%20had%20taken%20more%20wickets%20for%20India%20when%20he%20retired%3A%20266%20wickets%20in%2067%20Tests.%20Only%20two%20left-arm%20spinners%2C%20Derek%20Underwood%20of%20England%20and%20Daniel%20Vettori%20of%20New%20Zealand%2C%20have%20taken%20more%20Test%20wickets.%20But%20no%20one%20has%20brought%20more%20joy%20to%20the%20cricket%20purist%3B%20when%20Bedi%20came%20in%20to%20bowl%20in%20his%20resplendent%20blue%20or%20pink%20patka%2C%20you%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20be%20transfixed%20by%20his%20action%2C%20smooth%20and%20rich%20as%20the%20milk%20in%20his%20hometown.%20The%20English%20off-spinner%20Jim%20Laker%20once%20said%20that%20his%20idea%20of%20heaven%20was%20%E2%80%98sunshine%20at%20Lord%E2%80%99s%2C%20Ray%20Lindwall%2C%20the%20Australian%20fast%20bowler%2C%20bowling%20from%20one%20end%2C%20Bedi%20from%20the%20other%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20critics%20say%20Bedi%20bowled%20like%20a%20millionaire%2C%20often%20giving%20away%20too%20many%20runs%20in%20his%20search%20for%20wickets.%20This%20is%20statistically%20untrue%3B%20Bedi%20is%20second%20best%20to%20the%20West%20Indian%20Lance%20Gibbs%20in%20terms%20of%20bowling%20maiden%20overs%20per%20Test%20match.%20Bedi%20explains%20his%20approach%20of%20clapping%20after%20being%20hit%20for%20six.%20%E2%80%98You%20bowl%20to%20get%20a%20batsman%20out.%20If%20a%20Test%20batsman%20hits%20a%20few%20fours%20or%20sixes%20but%20I%20get%20him%20out%20for%2030%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20better%20than%20bowling%20defensively%20and%20allowing%20him%20to%20just%20bat%20on%20and%20on%20and%20score%20a%20hundred%3F%E2%80%99%20The%20attacking%20instinct%20played%20a%20bit%20part%20in%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20prominent%20role%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20first-ever%20overseas%20wins%20in%20Australia%2C%20West%20Indies%2C%20England%20and%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESir%20Don%20Bradman%20suggests%20that%20Bedi%20is%20among%20the%20greatest%20left-%20arm%20spinners%20of%20all%20time.%20In%20a%20fitting%20tribute%2C%20Bradman%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%98Bedi%20was%20a%20real%20study%20for%20the%20connoisseur.%20His%20ideal%20well-balanced%20run-up%20always%20brought%20him%20into%20the%20perfect%20delivery%20position.%20The%20ball%20was%20held%20well%20in%20the%20tips%20of%20long%2C%20almost%20delicate%20fingers%20which%20never%20seemed%20to%20get%20tired%2C%20but%20always%20retained%20great%20flexibility%20and%20control.%20There%20were%20regular%20but%20very%20subtle%20changes%20of%20pace%20%E2%80%93%20variations%20in%20flight%2C%20and%20always%20coupled%20with%20genuine%20spin.%20The%20end%20product%20was%20a%20delight%20to%20watch%20and%20I%20do%20not%20hesitate%20to%20rank%20Bedi%20among%20the%20finest%20bowlers%20of%20his%20type%20we%20have%20seen.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20Indian%20cricketer%20had%20received%20higher%20praise%20from%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20ultimate%20icon.%20But%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20true%20impact%20on%20Indian%20cricket%20lies%20not%20just%20in%20his%20contribution%20to%20the%20art%20of%20left-arm%20spin%20bowling%20but%20in%20the%20way%20he%20redefined%20the%20idea%20of%20leadership%20in%20Indian%20sport%20by%20putting%20player%20power%20above%20personal%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698123729000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24083208%2FF9JMon9WoAAF2wq.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fplayer-power-over-personal-success-bishan-singh-bedis-true-impact-on-indian-cricket%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bedi%E2%80%99s%20true%20impact%20on%20Indian%20cricket%20lies%20not%20just%20in%20his%20contribution%20to%20the%20art%20of%20left-arm%20spin%20bowling%20but%20in%20the%20way%20he%20redefined%20the%20idea%20of%20leadership%20in%20Indian%20sport%20by%20putting%20player%20power%20above%20personal%20success.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fplayer-power-over-personal-success-bishan-singh-bedis-true-impact-on-indian-cricket%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ten%20Years%20After%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Landmark%20Judgment%2C%20Dongria%20Kondhs%20in%20Niyamgiri%20Still%20Suffer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101346%2FNH1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20decade%20since%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fpdf%2FSupremeCourtReport%2F2013_v6_piv.pdf%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20landmark%20judgement%20in%202013%3C%2Fa%3E%20upholding%20the%20rights%20of%20%3Cem%3Egram%20sabhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20Niyamgiri%2C%20Rayagada%2C%20and%20Kalahandi%20(Odisha)%20against%20the%20conversion%20of%20forest%20land%20for%20proposed%20bauxite%20mining%20by%20Vedanta%20Alumina%20company.%20The%20judgment%20was%20a%20watershed%20moment%20for%20the%20decentralisation%20of%20power%2C%20grassroots%20democracy%2C%20and%20tribal%20rights%20over%20forest%20and%20land%20under%20the%20fifth%20scheduled%20areas%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20halted%20the%20advancement%20of%20bauxite%20mining%20on%20the%20top%20of%20Niyamgiri%20Hill%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20(a%20Particularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Group)%20continues%20to%20live%20there.%20However%2C%20despite%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20judgment%20protecting%20the%20community%20rights%20of%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20over%20Niyamgiri%2C%20their%20difficulties%20have%20continued.%20Government%20facilities%20are%20still%20a%20distant%20dream%2C%20and%20they%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20mental%20and%20emotional%20pressure%20of%20uncertainty%20and%20police%20surveillance%2C%20and%20violence%20in%20their%20day-to-day%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20infrastructure%20is%20still%20a%20distant%20dream%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20research%20team%2C%20we%20visited%20the%20Lakhpadar%20village%20situated%20on%20the%20top%20of%20Niyamgiri%20Hill.%20We%20travelled%20around%2010-15%20km%20from%20Lanjigarh%20to%20reach%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20village%20Phuldumer%2C%20which%20has%20a%20proper%20road%20and%20is%20situated%20on%20the%20base%20of%20Niygamgiri%20Hill.%20After%20that%2C%20we%20travelled%20another%20four%20kilometers%20on%20a%20steep%20metal%20road%20to%20reach%20a%20village%20called%20Tadijhola.%20From%20there%2C%20we%20climbed%20the%20forest%20and%20walked%20for%20one%20hour%20to%20reach%20another%20village%20called%20Lakhpadar.%20In%20between%2C%20we%20crossed%20as%20many%20as%20ten%20springs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESurrounded%20by%20a%20dense%20forest%2C%20the%20100%20metres%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20village%20has%20a%20newly%20constructed%20concrete%20road.%20There%20are%20around%2025%20houses%20constructed%20in%20two%20rows%2C%20with%20all%20houses%20covered%20with%20tin%20rooftops.%20The%20main%20street%20of%20the%20village%20is%20rough%2C%20with%20rock%20layers%2C%20and%20is%20steep%20on%20one%20side.%20The%20villagers%20depend%20on%20spring%20water%20connected%20through%20pipes%20and%20taps%3B%20the%20spring%20water%20is%20also%20used%20for%20bathing%20and%20other%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%202011%20census%2C%20the%20village%20has%20a%20population%20of%20270%20(115%20men%20and%20155%20women).%20It%20has%2059%20households%2C%20and%20the%20literacy%20rate%20is%200.47%25.%20There%20is%20no%20school%20or%20anganwadi%20centre%20in%20the%20village.%20They%20mostly%20depend%20upon%20traditional%20healthcare%20methods%2C%20and%20no%20healthcare%20center%20is%20nearby.%20The%20panchayat%20office%20Parsali%2C%20under%20Kalyangsingpur%20Bolk%2C%20district%20Rayagada%2C%20is%20around%2010%20km%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPhuldumer%2C%20Kunakadu%2C%20Tadijhola%2C%20and%20Lakhpadar%20are%20among%20the%2012%20villages%20where%20a%20gram%20sabha%20meeting%20was%20conducted%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order.%20The%20Dongria%20Kondh%20of%20the%20Niyamgiri%20Hills%20live%20in%20four%20community%20blocks%20%E2%80%93%20Muniguda%2C%20Raygada%2C%20and%20Kalyansingpur%20in%20Rayagada%20and%20Lanjigarh%20block%20in%20Kalahandi%20district.%20The%20majority%20of%20them%20live%20in%20the%20Rayagada%20district%2C%20as%20most%20of%20the%20Niyamgiri%20Hills%20come%20under%20the%20Rayagada%20district.%20These%20villages%20have%20very%20limited%20public%20infrastructure%20facilities%20like%20schools%2C%20healthcare%20centers%2C%20roads%2C%20transport%20services%2C%20markets%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20baseline%20survey%20by%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Research%20and%20Training%20Institute%20(2016)%20Odisha%20reveals%20that%20the%20total%20Dongria%20Kondh%20population%20in%20Rayagada%20district%20is%207%2C722%20(4%2C443%20women%20and%203%2C279%20men)%20living%20in%201%2C892%20families.%20They%20live%20in%2098%20villages%20with%20extremely%20minimal%20infrastructure%20facilities.%20For%20instance%2C%20only%2031%20of%20these%20villages%20have%20schools%2C%20while%2028%20villages%20have%20anganwadi%20centres.%20Only%2016%20villages%20are%20connected%20with%20motorable%20roads.%20The%20literacy%20rate%20among%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20is%2029%25%2C%20out%20of%20which%20the%20male%20literacy%20rate%20is%2024.5%25%20and%20the%20female%20literacy%20rate%20is%2015.9%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101559%2FNH3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22696%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101559%2FNH3.png%20696w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101559%2FNH3-300x186.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681485%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22432%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDemography%2C%20literacy%20and%20available%20basic%20infrastructure%20for%20Dongria%20Kondh%20in%20Niyamgiri%2C%20Rayagada.%20Source%3A%20SCs%20%26amp%3B%20STs%20Research%20Institute%20(SCSTRTI)%2C%20Government%20of%20Odisha%20(2016).%20Conservation-%20cum-%20Development%20Plan%20for%20Dangaria%20Kandha%20PVTG.%20DKDA%2C%20Kurli%2C%20Chatikona%2C%20Rayagada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20uncertain%20future%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Dongria%20Kondh%20depend%20upon%20shifting%20cultivation%20and%20collection%20of%20minor%20forest%20products%20for%20their%20livelihood.%20They%20have%20still%20maintained%20their%20unique%20way%20of%20life%2C%20maintaining%20their%20social%2C%20religious%20and%20cultural%20practices%20and%20beliefs%20which%20are%20different%20from%20the%20caste%20society.%20An%20activist%20who%20shares%20a%20close%20bond%20with%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cearlier%2C%20they%20were%20not%20participating%20in%20elections%20and%20were%20unaware%20of%20the%20police%20and%20judiciary%20system%2C%20as%20this%20system%20had%20not%20reached%20them.%20There%20was%20no%20road%20and%20connectivity%2C%20no%20school%20and%20anganwadi%20even%20today.%20However%2C%20after%20Vedanta%20came%20to%20Niyamgiri%20they%20protested%20and%20came%20into%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20police%2C%20judiciary%20and%20outside%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELada%20Sikaka%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20and%20president%20of%20Niyamgiri%20Suraksha%20Samiti%2C%20recalled%20their%20protest%20against%20the%20mining%20and%20life%20thereafter%20with%20pain.%20He%20said%20that%20till%20now%2C%20they%20have%20not%20allowed%20Vedanta%20to%20mine%20on%20their%20sacred%20land%2C%20and%20he%20is%20hopeful%20that%20the%20next%20generation%20will%20continue%20to%20save%20their%20land.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20living%20in%20this%20forest%20for%20generations.%20This%20is%20our%20%3Cem%3Emata%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mother)%20that%20gives%20us%20food%2C%20a%20living%2C%20and%20water.%20If%20the%20company%20displaces%20us%2C%20we%20will%20die.%20If%20our%20%3Cem%3Emata%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20erased%2C%20then%20how%20can%20we%20live%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20company%20came%20to%20the%20area%2C%20their%20struggles%20have%20doubled%2C%20Sikaka%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20fought%20and%20we%20won.%20The%20company%20had%20come%20and%20started%20some%20work%20near%20our%20sacred%20place%20where%20we%20worship%20Niyam%20Raja%20Niyam%20God)%20and%20we%20had%20no%20other%20choice%20than%20to%20oppose%20it%20strongly%2C%E2%80%9D%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20is%20still%20worried%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20company%20taking%20over%20their%20sacred%20hill.%20Organising%20against%20the%20Vedanta%20project%2C%20and%20the%20turmoil%20and%20uncertainty%20that%20brought%2C%20meant%20they%20had%20to%20take%20time%20away%20from%20their%20daily%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101501%2FNH2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101501%2FNH2.png%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24101501%2FNH2-300x186.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681484%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Dongria%20Kondh%20village%20in%20Niyamgiri%20Hill.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContinuous%20police%20surveillance%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2029%2C%20there%20was%20news%20in%20the%20evening%20that%20environmental%20activist%20Prafulla%20Samantara%20had%20been%20kidnapped%20from%20a%20private%20lodge%20in%20the%20district%20headquarter%20Rayagada%20and%20was%20released%C2%A0%20in%20Berhamapur%2C%20which%20is%20205%20km%20away.%20He%20had%20come%20to%20meet%20the%20arrested%20leaders%20of%20the%20Niyamgiri%20Surakha%20Samiti%20and%20was%20supposed%20to%20address%20a%20press%20conference%20after%20that.%20He%20alleged%20that%20his%20unlawful%20detention%20was%20done%20either%20by%20the%20police%20or%20goons%20hired%20by%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20August%209%2C%20when%20the%20whole%20world%20was%20celebrating%20World%20Indigenous%20Day%2C%20the%20Dongria%20Kondhs%20of%20Niyamgiri%20Hill%20and%20their%20supporters%20were%20arrested%20and%20slapped%20with%20the%20UAPA%20by%20the%20Odisha%20police%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20attending%20a%20celebration%20and%20protest%20gathering.%20Those%20who%20were%20charged%20include%20Lada%20Sikaka%2C%20Drenju%20Krushka%2C%20Manu%20Sikaka%20and%20Saamba%20Huika%20(all%20from%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%20community)%20and%20their%20supporters%20like%20Lingaraj%20Azad%2C%20Upendra%20Bag%20and%20Lenin%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELingaraj%20Azad%2C%20an%20activist%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Niyamgiri%20Suraksha%20Samiti%2C%20said%20that%20just%20before%20World%20Indigenous%20Day%2C%20two%20Dongria%20Kondh%20young%20men%20were%20picked%20up%20while%20they%20were%20on%20their%20way%20home%20from%20shopping.%20After%20four%20or%20five%20days%20of%20protest%2C%20villagers%20came%20to%20know%20that%20they%20had%20been%20detained%20by%20the%20police%2C%20who%20initially%20denied%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20matter.%20Finally%2C%20they%20released%20one%20youth%2C%20while%20the%20other%20was%20charged%20in%20a%20rape%20case.%20Surprisingly%2C%20neither%20he%20nor%20anyone%20else%20knows%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20and%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20in%20the%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELingaraj%20Azad%20alleged%20that%20police%20framed%20innocent%20Dongria%20Kondhs%20and%20their%20supporters%20under%20false%20charges%2C%20and%20used%20the%20draconian%20UAPA%20to%20try%20and%20silence%20them.%20He%20counts%C2%A0%20more%20than%2020%20who%20have%20been%20falsely%20framed%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Lada%20Sikaka%2C%20police%20surveillance%20and%20violence%20began%20only%20after%20Vedanta%20came%20to%20Lanjigarh%20and%20proposed%20to%20mine%20on%20their%20land.%20He%20has%20been%20arrested%20thrice%20by%20the%20police%20under%20various%20charges%20that%20he%20does%20not%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWay%20forward%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20into%20the%20socio-economic%20situation%20of%20Dongria%20Kondhs%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20basic%20public%20infrastructure%20in%20Niyamgiri%2C%20and%20the%20police%20violence%2C%20the%20question%20that%20comes%20to%20mind%20is%2C%20how%20sensitive%20is%20the%20state%20police%20while%20dealing%20with%20a%20Particularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Group%20like%20the%20Dongria%20Kondh%3F%20More%20than%20the%20police%2C%20what%20they%20needed%20was%20a%20teacher%2C%20an%20anganwadi%20and%20road%20and%20transportation%20infrastructure.%20The%20police%20cannot%20bring%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr%20