on%20to%20become%20a%20much%20sought-after%20exercise%20and%20a%20learning%20experience%20for%20all%20involved.%20Having%20completed%20more%20than%2025%20years%2C%20the%20summer%20camp%20in%20Bengaluru%20hit%20its%20first%20roadblock%20with%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20in%202020%2C%20and%20later%20with%20Sudha%E2%80%99s%20progressing%20ailment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20has%20been%20living%20with%20Multiple%20Sclerosis%20for%20the%20last%2052%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMultiple%20Sclerosis%20(MS)%20is%20a%20potentially%20disabling%20disease%20of%20the%20brain%20and%20spinal%20cord%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Mayo%20Clinic.%20Undeterred%20and%20enthusiastic%2C%20Sudha%20continued%20giving%20back%20to%20the%20community%20by%20opening%20her%20home%20to%20numerous%20kids%20and%20teachers%20over%20the%20years%20to%20forge%20a%20bond%20in%20creativity%2C%20friendship%20and%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeated%20around%20Sudha%20and%20recollecting%20the%20happy%20times%2C%20teachers%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20Jayashree%20Prasad%2C%20Srimathi%20K%20Singh%20and%20Mamatha%20talk%20about%20how%20important%20these%20summer%20camps%20were%20for%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSudha%20was%20the%20fulcrum%20around%20which%20we%20functioned%2C%20we%20love%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20teachers%20say%2C%20echoing%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kids%20at%20the%20camp%20participating%20in%20an%20event.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-me