0compound%2C%20or%20perhaps%20a%20library.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20idea%20soon%20metamorphosed%20into%20a%20summer%20camp%20for%20children.%20Located%20at%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Malleswaram%2C%20which%20was%20thrown%20open%20to%20the%20children%2C%20it%20was%20a%20big%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGreatly%20inspired%20by%20Sudha%2C%20teachers%20here%20worked%20voluntarily.%20Many%20were%20known%20to%20her%2C%20some%20whose%20children%20had%20been%20tutored%20by%20her.%20Her%20wisdom%2C%20patient%20listening%2C%20counselling%2C%20and%20encouragement%20to%20the%20teachers%2C%20proved%20a%20big%20motivating%20factor%20for%20the%20flock%20that%20increased%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSudha%20has%20been%20an%20inspiration%20for%20the%20entire%20MS%20community.%20The%20consistent%20work%20she%20put%20into%20designing%20the%20summer%20workshop%20for%20kids%20through%20meticulous%20planning%2C%20networking%20and%20creativity%20is%20no%20less%20than%20a%20learning%20opportunity%20for%20any%20business%20school%20student.%20Her%20positive%20attitude%20and%20demeanour%20is%20infectious%20and%20you%20cannot%20say%20no%20to%20a%20request%20from%20Sudha%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%C2%A0A%20Kala%2C%20managing%20committee%20member%2C%20Multiple%20Sclerosis%20Society%20of%20India%20(MSSI)%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20Chapter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20though%20the%20camps%20have%20been%20discontinued%2C%20the%20students%20and%20teachers%20do%20not%20miss%20an%20opportunity%20to%20drop%20in%20and%20spend%20time%20with%20their%20mentor.%20Around%20100%20teachers%20volunteered%20at%20the%20summer%20camp%20over%20the%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0010_11zon-1698072771.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Located%20at%20the%