0boosted%20his%20morale%20and%20opened%20up%20doors%20for%20him%20at%20a%20standup%20comedy%20club%20in%20Bay%20Area%2C%20California%2C%20called%20%E2%80%98Building%2018%E2%80%99.%20This%20kicked%20off%20the%2039-year-old%E2%80%99s%20stint%20as%20a%20comedian.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20joined%20Building%2018%20in%20May%202020%20and%20learnt%20tips%20and%20tricks%20on%20how%20to%20write%20a%20script%2C%20how%20to%20deliver%20a%20punch%2C%20what%20is%20stand-up%20comedy%20and%20much%20more.%20I%20found%20this%20to%20be%20much%20more%20difficult%20than%20medicine%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20first%20standup%20show%20at%20the%20club%2C%20Dr%20Pal%20describes%20the%20experience%20as%20%E2%80%9Cincomparable%E2%80%9D.%20He%20says%20he%20spent%20hours%20preparing%20for%20his%2010-minute%20set%2C%20where%20he%20spoke%20about%20many%20serious%20medical%20issues%20in%20a%20comical%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20grab%20this%20chance%20that%20life%20had%20given%20him%2C%20the%20doctor%20dove%20head%20first%20into%20comedy%2C%20creating%20reels%20and%20videos%2C%20and%20doing%20shows.%20Today%2C%20he%20does%20his%20%E2%80%98medcom%E2%80%99%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%20in%20the%20US%2C%20India%2C%20Malaysia%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20punchline%20for%20a%20health%20tip%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5_1yhDaDZfA%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3