es%20up%20before%20sunrise%20only%20to%20watch%20his%20favourite%20hero%E2%80%99s%20first-day-first-show%20movie%20in%20the%20theatre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20sleeping%20two%20hours%20before%20sunrise%20these%20days!%20All%20the%20phones%20before%20bed%20neutralise%20the%20effects%20of%20melatonin%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20you%20sleep.%20We%20are%20also%20doing%20desk%20jobs%20without%20any%20movement.%20Try%20working%20and%20eating%20only%20between%20sunrise%20and%20sunset.%20This%20will%20help%20the%20circadian%20rhythm%20of%20the%20body.%20Have%20a%20winding%20routine%20post%20sunset%20and%20give%20rest%20to%20your%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Pal%20further%20urges%20everyone%20to%20lead%20a%20balanced%20life%20and%20not%20compromise%20on%20health.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20make%20this%20too%20complicated.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20eat%20quinoa%20or%20expensive%20organic%20food.%20Just%20follow%20your%20ancestors%20and%20keep%20it%20simple%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202123px)%20100vw%2C%202123px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222123%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Pal%20imparts%20crucial%20medical%20information%20through%20his%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%20worldwide.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-scaled.jpg%202123w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-249x300.jpg%20249w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-500x603.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-768x926.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-1274x1536.jpg%201274w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-1698x2048.jpg%201698w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-150x181.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332866%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Pal%20imparts%20crucial%20medical%20information%20through%20his%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%20worldwide.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ER%20Suguna%2C%20who%20follows%20Dr%20Pal%20on%20YouTube%2C%20says%20that%20she%20has%20become%20healthier%20after%20following%20his%20videos.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20PCOS%20and%20was%20having%20a%20hard%20time%20losing%20weight.%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20get%20my%20periods%20regularly.%20I%20started%20following%20intermittent%20fasting%20and%20moving%20throughout%20the%20day%20after%20watching%20Dr%20Pal%E2%80%99s%20videos.%20The%20change%20has%20been%20immense.%20Over%20the%20past%2014%20months%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20regularise%20my%20periods%20and%20have%20much%20better%20stamina%20and%20energy%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suguna.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Pal%20shares%20that%20his%20idea%20is%20to%20give%20tips%20and%20tricks%20in%20an%20interactive%2C%20interesting%20way%2C%20without%20making%20it%20feel%20like%20a%20lecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20love%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20comes%20from%20making%20people%20laugh.%20So%20many%20come%20up%20to%20me%20and%20share%20the%20changes%20in%20their%20lives%20after%20following%20my%20tips.%20They%20have%20tears%20in%20their%20eyes%20as%20they%20share%20their%20stories.%20It%20just%20leaves%20me%20awestruck.%20I%20just%20want%20people%20to%20get%20healthier%20and%20receive%20fewer%20patients%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20his%20work%20in%20weight%20loss%2C%20a%20particular%20incident%20deeply%20touched%20the%20gastroenterologist.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20initial%20videos%2C%20he%20addressed%20the%20safety%20of%20COVID-19%20vaccines%2C%20prompting%20an%20elderly%20woman%20from%20Madurai%20to%20receive%20the%20vaccine.%20%E2%80%9CI%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20a%20woman%20in%20Thootukudi.%20She%20had%20lost%20her%20father%20to%20COVID%20as%20the%20vaccine%20was%20not%20available%20then.%20She%20said%20that%20her%20mother%20took%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326043%2Ftwo-moms-serve-the-magic-of-home-cooked-eco-friendly-dabbas-to-thousands-in-london%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evaccine%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20seeing%20my%20video.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98At%20least%2C%20I%20have%20my%20mother%20today%2C%20thanks%20to%20you%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Pal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20can%20change%20somebody%E2%80%99s%20life%20sitting%20in%20Sacramento%2C%20talking%20to%20a%20camera%2C%20why%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20I%20do%20it%3F%20It%20is%20truly%20satisfying%20as%20well%20as%20fun%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr%20Pal%20contributes%20his%20social%20media%20earnings%20to%20the%20Aishwaryam%20Trust.%20You%20can%20contribute%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faishwaryamtrust.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20Dr%20Palaniappan%20Manickam%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698070900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F5_1yhDaDZfA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332843%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Palaniappan%20Manickam%2C%20known%20as%20Dr%20Pal%2C%20effectively%20conveys%20important%20medical%20information%20using%20humour%20or%2