ldren%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail.%20Put%20in%20your%20best%2C%20work%20hard%2C%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20lose%20heart%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20what%20you%20want%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331067%2Framji-swaminathan-craftizan-miniature-models-of-isro-rockets-satellites-chandrayaan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%20Indians%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20achieved%20success%20after%20failing%20to%20get%20into%20the%20career%20they%20wanted.%20Dr%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20an%20aerospace%20scientist%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20former%20President%2C%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20fighter%20pilot%2C%20but%20failed%20to%20get%20through%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20by%20a%20whisker.%20He%20did%20not%20give%20up%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20India%20got%20a%20missile%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20concurs%2C%20and%20says%20that%20we%20all%20went%20through%20failures%20at%20one%20point%20in%20our%20lives%20and%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20all%20overcome%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLife%20is%20very%20big.%20You%20will%20feel%20bad%20for%20that%20moment%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20into%20an%20IIT%20or%20medical%20college.%20There%20are%20100%20more%20avenues.%20Explore%20them.%20One%20day%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20look%20back%20at%20this%20and%20laugh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20hopefully.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698069242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FKOta-1-1698067807.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332810%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%2025%20students%20dying%20by%20suicide%20in%20the%20past%2010%20months%20in%20Kota%2C%20alarm%20bells%20have%20once%20again%20been%20set%20off%20in%20the%20country%20over%20the%20students'%20mental%20healt