0to%20vest%20herself%20more%20fully%20into%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20completed%20her%20work%20in%2048%20villages%20in%20Beed%2C%20Nutanben%20made%20her%20way%20to%20Jalna%20in%20July-August%202016%2C%20where%20she%20began%20working%20with%20her%20NGO%20%E2%80%98Samast%20Mahajan%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20she%20is%20a%20trustee%20based%20out%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20on%20desilting%20water%20bodies%20and%20rejuvenating%20water%20sources%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20local%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20675px)%20100vw%2C%20675px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20locals%20in%20Jalna%20contributed%20their%20bit%20by%20providing%20the%20diesel.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665.jpg%20675w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC01286_11zon-1697801665-150x112.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22506%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20locals%20in%20Jalna%20contributed%20their%20bit%20by%20providing%20the%20diesel.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJalna%E2%80%99s%20transformation%3A%20From%20250%20tankers%20a%20day%20to%20nil%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20NGO%2C%20headquartered%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20provided%20the%20rental%20costs%20of%20the%20expensive%20machines%20required%20for%20the%20job%20through%20its%20partnership%20with%20the%20A.T.E.%20Chandra%20foundation%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20while%20the%20locals%20contributed%20their%20bit%20by%20providing%20the%20diesel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20team%20worked%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20translated%20into%20results%20on%20the%20ground.%20Although%20her%20NGO%20had%20been%20set%20up%20many%20years%20ago%20with%20the%20purpose%20of%20focussing%20on%20animal%20care%2C%20it%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20primarily%20focussed%20on%20saving%20and%20improving%20human%20lives%20in%20a%20country%20prone%20to%20natural%20and%20manmade%20calamities%20where%20government%20intervention%20is%20often%20inadequate%20or%20even%20absent.%20Human%20beings%2C%20at%20some%20level%2C%20took%20precedence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Nutanben%20and%20her%20team%20began%20working%20in%20around%20330-odd%20villages%20and%20%3Cem%3Etalukas%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20comprise%20the%20Jalna%20district%2C%20the%20situation%20was%20not%20much%20better%20than%20it%20was%20in%20Beed.%20Water%20was%20very%20scarce%2C%20most%20of%20the%20water%20bodies%20in%20the%20region%20were%20silted%20up%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288219%2Fafter-visiting-drought-prone-villages-23-yo-plants-3-lakh-trees-in-three-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebone%20dry%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20tankers%20were%20the%20only%20way%20of%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20started%20working%2C%20each%20%3Cem%3Etehsil%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%208%20in%20Jalna%20district%20%E2%80%94%20survived%20on%20250%20tankers%20per%20day.%20Farmers%20were%20barely%20producing%20anything%20since%20there%20was%20no%20water%20for%20farming%3B%20meeting%20the%20basic%20consumption%20needs%20was%20a%20struggle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20when%20the%20team%20arrived%20in%20the%20district%2C%20villagers%20and%20locals%20were%20highly%20sceptical%20on%20whether%20such%20work%20could%20be%20done%20with%20community%20participation%20and%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20an%20NGO.%C2%A0%3C%2