er%20the%20years%2C%20but%20now%20the%20focus%20is%20squarely%20back%20on%20how%20one%20can%20use%20these%20grains%20in%20their%20diet%20and%20farmers%20are%20switching%20back%20to%20growing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20change%20are%20Indians%20who%20are%20bringing%20millets%20back%20to%20the%20spotlight%20through%20their%20innovations.%20They%20are%20delivering%20millets%20in%20new%2C%20interesting%20ways%2C%20helping%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20five%20Indians%20championing%20the%20humble%20grain%20through%20their%20startups%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVeer%20Shetty%20Biradar%2C%20SS%20Bhavani%20Foods%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20583px)%20100vw%2C%20583px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22583%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Veer%20Shetty%20Biradar%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186.jpeg%20583w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186-178x300.jpeg%20178w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186-500x843.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-03-02-at-10.05.13-AM-1646229186-150x253.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-277461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22983%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVeer%20Shetty%20Biradar%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Millet%20Man.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20family%20o